# eof-multiple-entries

## Input

```
a 1
b 2
```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..7
  ENTRY@0..4
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    INTEGER@2..3
      NUMERAL@2..3 "1"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
  ENTRY@4..7
    WORD_KEY@4..5
      WORD@4..5 "b"
    SPACE@5..6 " "
    INTEGER@6..7
      NUMERAL@6..7 "2"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: Integer {
                sign: none,
                numeral: NUMERAL@2..3 "1",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@4..5 "b",
            },
            value: Integer {
                sign: none,
                numeral: NUMERAL@6..7 "2",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

